Ctrl+A          Apply transformation, rotation, scale to the object and clear its value
Ctrl+P          Make the objects that have been selected be the sons of the last selected object
Alt+P           Make the objects leave parent
A               Select all objects in the scene
N               Show the properties of the selected object
Space           Quick action search, often use it for import models
Ctrl+Alt+U      Open the settings
Ctrl+O          Open blender file
Shift+F         roaming around the scene
Numpad 0        preview using the main camera